snippet.title: Voyagers of Nera - Game Trailer | Wholesome Snack 2023: Game Awards Edition
snippet.description:
Your voyage starts now.

​​Nera, a world of endless beauty, magic and wonder, needs our protection. The chaotic oceans change and shift, while corruption threatens the islands and villages—only you can restore the balance. Gather your fellow Runeborn, awaken the spirit of your newborn island, and harness the world around you to build a new home together.

Welcome to Voyagers of Nera, a co-op survival-crafting game for up to 16 players that’s coming to Early Access in 2024. Bond with your living island, skim on the ever-shifting oceans around you, and shape a flourishing village with your friends.

Voyagers of Nera is available on the Steam store for wishlist: https://bit.ly/VoyagersofNeraSteam

Visit our website voyagersofnera.com and keep an eye on our social channels for more details about the game! 
http://twitter.com/voyagersofnera
http://tiktok.com/@voyagersofnera 
http://instagram.com/voyagersofnera

Check out our Discord server to join in on the conversation: http://discord.gg/voyagersofnera
